* When Lakeflow\nDeclarative Fits Best
** Standardized ETL
***_ Schema evolution
***_ Slowly changing dimensions
***_ Reduces boilerplate code
** Data Quality
***_ Built-in expectations
***_ Quality rules in pipeline def
***_ Tracks violations
** Auto Dependency Mgmt
***_ Analyzes table relationships
***_ Correct execution order
***_ Refreshes affected tables
** Operational Visibility
***_ Lineage tracking
***_ Execution graphs
***_ Monitoring dashboards
